= 3 BUILD INSTRUCTIONS =================================================

To build IMSEQ, you will need

 * Cmake 2.8.2 or newer
 * A C++ 11 compliant C++ compiler such as gcc 2.7
 * zlib header files, otherwise your binary will not be able to read
   gzip compressed FASTQ / FASTA files

Invoke the following commands to build IMSEQ:

$ cmake ./seqan_minimal/
$ make

If you do not want to use your systems default C++ compiler, you can specify
the path to your C++ compiler as shown in this example:

$ cmake -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=/usr/bin/g++-4.8 ./seqan_minimal/
$ make

You will find your 'imseq' binary in the 'bin' folder.
